						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying near the Māriyammaṉ shrine.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Viśvāvasu, Śrāvaṇa • • • • .</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records imprecations against the violation of grants made to Brāhmaṇas and [temples] by Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Rāmarāja Chinna-Timma Mahārāja.</p>						

